OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIsolated
OL,6,Fshowers will ease through this
OL,7,Fevening, allowing it to become dry and
OL,8,Fclear across the country overnight.
OL,9,FTurning chilly under the clear skies
OL,10,Fwith a few mist and fog patches
OL,11,Fpossible and a touch of frost in the
OL,12,Fcountryside.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FAny mist or fog will quickly
OL,15,Fclear in the morning. Staying dry with
OL,16,Fsunny spells at first, but cloud
OL,17,Flikely increasing during the afternoon
OL,18,Fin the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
